# Test Case Count Targets

Use these as minimum quality gates.

| Feature Complexity | Minimum Cases | Typical Range |
|-------------------|---------------|---------------|
| Simple form | 8 | 8-15 |
| Auth flow | 20 | 20-35 |
| CRUD feature | 15 | 15-25 |
| Payment or checkout | 30 | 30-50 |
| File upload | 12 | 12-20 |
| Search or filter | 10 | 10-18 |
| Listing with pagination | 10 | 10-18 |
| Multi-step workflow | 20 | 20-40 |
| Role-based permissions | 12 | 12-25 |
| API endpoint | 10 | 10-20 |
| Data migration or calculation | 12 | 12-25 |

If output is below the minimum, explain why or revisit the requirements analysis.

